WEBVTT

00:00:00.389 --> 00:00:02.333
Track 03.08

00:00:04.667 --> 00:00:05.635
Waiter: Good afternoon

00:00:05.714 --> 00:00:07.000
Sam: Hello.

00:00:07.063 --> 00:00:09.523
I’d like a cup of tea, please.

00:00:09.762 --> 00:00:11.761
Waiter: Sure. And to eat?

00:00:12.240 --> 00:00:15.225
Sam: I’d like a cheese sandwich, please.

00:00:15.717 --> 00:00:16.844
Waiter: With tomato?

00:00:17.240 --> 00:00:18.701
Sam: No, thanks.

00:00:18.828 --> 00:00:21.713
And can I have some chocolate cake

00:00:21.757 --> 00:00:24.350
and a glass of water too, please?

00:00:24.808 --> 00:00:25.787
Waiter: Of course!

00:00:26.003 --> 00:00:27.899
That’s £11, please.

00:00:28.269 --> 00:00:30.253
Sam: OK. Here you are.

00:00:30.862 --> 00:00:31.753
Waiter: Thank you.